[head=2]Mission Overview[/head]
[bold]Location:[/bold]
 Unmarked Vault, coordinates approximately 5 miles west of Inside Black-Mountains.

[bold]Objective:[/bold] Investigate distress signals originating from a suspected Vault-Tec installation. Assess conditions, recover salvageable resources, and neutralize hostile threats.

